SBADescriptor.Name: Install Hv.Helper module for Horizon View scripts
SBADescriptor.Description: For using Horizon View scripts the Hv.Helper module is required. This script installs the module (version 1.1) on the target machine (for all users). By default an existing module is NOT overwritten. If Overwrite = True is specified the existing module will be overwritten. The module is embedded in the script. The version is 1.1

SBAArgumentDescriptor.ValidationError: Please choose wether to overwrite an existing Hv.Helper module if it is alreay installed. Enter 'True' if you want to do this, default is 'False'
